# Copied into the container by scripts/test-pkg-container.sh (no @TOKEN@ to fill).
# "fast_test" tweaks applied to every test container: make source builds feasible
# and fast without relying on the binhost. A prebuilt GHC (dev-lang/ghc[binary],
# fetched from gentoo mirrors) avoids the multi-hour source bootstrap that the
# haskell toolchain (dev-util/shellcheck) would otherwise need.
dev-lang/ghc binary
